title: NFS Underground 2 With Cheats/Widescreen Patch and More
description:
Minimum System Requirements:

CPU:	Intel Pentium III (or equivalent) CPU running at 933MHz or higher
RAM:	256 MB
VGA:	32MB DirectX 9.0c compatible video card (Geforce2 or higher) using a
supported chipset (see below)
ATI Radeon 7500 or greater
NVIDIA GeForce2 or greater
DX:	DirectX 9.0c
OS:	Windows 98, 98 Second Edition, ME, 2000 Professional, XP Professiona <a href="
http://gamesystemrequirements.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://gamesystemrequirements.com/</a>
HDD:	900 MB of HD space
Sound:	DirectX compatible Sound Card
ODD:	8X CD-ROM
Network:	For Online play a Network card is required for broadband connectivity
Recommended peripheral:	DirectX compatible Controller or Keyboard

1. Burn or mount with daemon tools.
2. Install the game.
3. Use the keygen in /Crack directory to generate your own key.
4. Copy over cracked executables from /Crack directory to your install directory.
5. Play the game.
6. Included in the NFSU2.iso is a folder called Extras, open that up for a

Widescreen Patch, a Texture Mod, Cheats, Walkthrough, Tutorial, and a Map of all shop locations.
